{"tid":154743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】神秘會議 揭林鄭親割五十萬呎地益馬會","createTime":"2017-03-13T13:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T01:27:04.000Z","uid":44358,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b817f67df62cb1342c9cb9d827b940fedf4fb464","tid":154743,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥推西九故宮大計，成為「女版689」官場上盡地一鋪、向中央獻媚的成績表，博上特首寶座。 <br />\n<br />\n而一鋪捐三十五億，鼎力支持林鄭建宮的，就是馬會。 <br />\n<br />\n馬會前主席夏佳理擔任林鄭的競選辦主席團成員；香港賽馬會見習騎師學校校長陳念慈亦是林鄭競選辦的副主任。 <br />\n<br />\n究竟馬會、林鄭有甚麼關係？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_486833_0&amp;i=20170313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_486833_0%26i%3D20170313&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=50aa9ebd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_486833_0%26i%3D20170313&h=12eef1c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_486833_0&amp;i=20170313</a>"},{"pid":"53aa6c340d342681d669d9c11ec5b3260b1b1282","tid":154743,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"推,屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035db9ea1677c64001cf8f11cb183de4b8497d88","tid":154743,"uid":53677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1b7c209557cacc973e4f0a403efe7f84d8a4f6","tid":154743,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"蘋果發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji